<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Secondary Bureau Blackout</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: sans-serif; background-color: #f0f4f8; color: #1a202c; padding: 20px; line-height: 1.6; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background: white; padding: 30px; border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }
        h1 { text-align: center; color: #2d3748; }
        .bureau-card { border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .bureau-name { font-weight: bold; font-size: 1.2rem; display: block; margin-bottom: 10px; }
        .btn { display: inline-block; background: #2563eb; color: white; padding: 10px 20px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 15px; }
        .btn:hover { background: #1e40af; }
        .script-box { background: #f7fafc; border-left: 4px solid #60a5fa; padding: 15px; font-size: 0.9rem; color: #4a5568; }
        .note { font-size: 0.8rem; color: #718096; margin-top: 10px; font-style: italic; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="container">
        <h1>Bureau Blackout System</h1>
        <p style="text-align: center;">Freeze these bureaus before mailing your letters.</p>

        <div class="bureau-card">
            <span class="bureau-name">1. LEXISNEXIS</span>
            <a href="https://consumer.risk.lexisnexis.com/freeze" target="_blank" class="btn">Open Freeze Portal</a>
            <div class="script-box">
                <strong>Script:</strong> "I am requesting a security freeze on my consumer report under the FCRA. My info: [Full Name], [SSN], [Address]."
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bureau-card">
            <span class="bureau-name">2. SAGESTREAM</span>
            <a href="https://www.sagestreamllc.com/security-freeze/" target="_blank" class="btn">Open Freeze Portal</a>
            <div class="script-box">
                <strong>Script:</strong> "I am requesting a security freeze on my SageStream/Invisis file immediately. Info: [Full Name], [SSN], [Address]."
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bureau-card">
            <span class="bureau-name">3. INNOVIS</span>
            <a href="https://www.innovis.com/securityFreeze/index" target="_blank" class="btn">Open Freeze Portal</a>
            <div class="script-box">
                <strong>Script:</strong> "Please place a security freeze on my Innovis credit report. Details: [Full Name], [SSN], [Address]."
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bureau-card">
            <span class="bureau-name">4. ARS</span>
            <a href="https://www.ars-consumertools.com/" target="_blank" class="btn">Open Freeze Portal</a>
            <div class="script-box">
                <strong>Script:</strong> "I am exercising my rights under the FCRA to freeze my report with ARS. Info: [Full Name], [SSN], [Address]."
            </div>
        </div>

        <p class="note">Manual Copy: Highlight the text above and copy (Ctrl+C) to use in the portals.</p>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
